{"tid":1429252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾Jackson微博做護旗手惹不滿　網民發起月底向GOT7「接機」","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:08:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":160,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cd294add277fb65cc3e6149d43fd2b098e7c72","tid":1429252,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3127771/org/45acce43be4ef05b268045c9b329e9fb.jpg/fbJrmbl07MiQ-l5G_nrbxIyNL5lyi1CxE0Ka4hNCmuI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3127771%2Forg%2F45acce43be4ef05b268045c9b329e9fb.jpg%2FfbJrmbl07MiQ-l5G_nrbxIyNL5lyi1CxE0Ka4hNCmuI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2578b5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「反修例」引起的紛爭愈演愈烈，上星期六（3日）更有示威者拆下尖沙咀天星碼頭旗杆的 國旗再拋落海，有記者拍到國旗在海上漂流的畫面，因而引起內地網民的強烈批評。近日《人民日報》就在微博發起「#五星紅旗有14億護旗手#」的活動，自稱香港土成土長的Jackson王嘉爾亦有轉發，令香港網民及部分粉絲非常不滿。<br />\n<br />\n 除了Jackson外，不少香港藝人都有轉發護旗手活動，包括陳小春及Angelababy等。尤其周一（5/8）進行「8.5罷工」，因此王嘉爾轉發微博後，令不少粉絲反感。在連登討論區「X嘉爾出賣港人」的帖子中，有網民講到Jackson將隨組合GOT7於月尾來港開演唱會，提議到機場進行「接機」活動。有網民更主動貼出GOT7來港的航班編號，除了準備印有出賣香港字樣的Banner外，亦將用韓英兩語讀出口號，好讓GOT7成員了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n 網民IG留負評 Jackson沒有回應但刪留言<br />\n<br />\n 未知接機活動落實與否前，昨日已有一批網民到Jackson個人IG留言以示不滿，當中包括「可恥」、「失望」和粗言穢語的字眼。另外亦有粉絲表示曾經也非常欣賞王嘉爾，認為不表態並沒問題，可是背棄香港人的行為就令人非常失望，而Jackson沒有公開回應事件，而事後亦已將所有負面留言刪走，不過到底這個IG帳戶是否由他一個人管理，則得不而 知。2014年Jackson以首個港人韓星的身份在韓國出道，出道初期都會強調自己香港人的 身份。可是2016年開始打入中國市場後，在各種因素下，王嘉爾不時會自稱「來自中國」，一直在香港備受爭議。<br />\n<br />\n 不過當然都有不少粉絲撐偶像，到Jackson的IG留言為他打氣。有粉絲表示香港是一個能夠容納各種聲音的社會，即使大部人不接受王嘉爾，一班真正的粉絲都會繼續為他應援。粉絲亦希望大眾能欣賞Jackson的努力，或者拋開國藉和立場集中在他的作品上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/360732/%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BEjackson%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%81%9A%E8%AD%B7%E6%97%97%E6%89%8B%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%90%91got7-%E6%8E%A5%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F360732%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%2588%25BEjackson%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2590%2591got7-%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25A9%259F&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=ab184ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/360732/%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BEjackson%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%81%9A%E8%AD%B7%E6%97%97%E6%89%8B%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%90%91got7-%E6%8E%A5%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n支那01報導已轉載到PTT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7240fd79d3dd56621941b25df5a72c229015839a","tid":1429252,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"PTT LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1565181641.A.ED7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1565181641.A.ED7.html&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=c4737ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1565181641.A.ED7.html</a>"},{"pid":"050714b9e3e36756d413251f02877aec88ee2c88","tid":1429252,"uid":132587,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"條撚屌宜家基本上同got7無曬關係架啦<br />\n之前仲要成日扮團隊行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431522607a880feeaae6bf53dbaa66cec6935469","tid":1429252,"uid":76632,"like":145,"dislike":0,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:52:03.0